    </tr>
  </table>
<p>Table `language`</p>
  <ul class="table-columns">
      <li> `language_id` - Unique identifier for each language.</li>
      <li> `name` - Language name.</li>
      <li> `last_update` - Timestamp indicating when the record was last updated.</li> 
